Rare is an open source alternative for Epic Games Launcher, using '''Legendary'''. It provides a graphical interface for Legendary, a command line alternative to Epic Games launcher, written in '''PySide6'''. Rare aims to be a lightweight and feature-full experience, integrating seamlessly with Legendary. The project is developed in '''Python''' and supports most major platforms.

== Overview ==
Rare is designed to be a native application that runs on major platforms, allowing users to enjoy their games without the need for the Epic Games Launcher. The project is built on top of Legendary, a command line alternative to the Epic Games Launcher, and provides a graphical interface for users to interact with.

=== Why Rare? ===
The reasons for using Rare include:
* '''Native support''': Rare runs natively on most major platforms.
* '''Lightweight''': Rare is designed to be as lightweight as possible while still offering a feature-full experience.
* '''Seamless integration''': Rare integrates seamlessly with Legendary, as both projects are developed in '''Python'''.
* '''Packages''': Rare provides access to a wide range of packages.

== Features ==
Rare offers a range of features, including:
* A graphical interface for Legendary
* Support for most major platforms
* A lightweight and feature-full experience
* Seamless integration with Legendary
* Access to a wide range of packages

